                    <h2>Careers with ClearCube</h2>
                        <div class="left">
                        <p>ClearCube is in high growth mode. If you're seeking a rewarding career opportunity with a growing company that is a catalyst in the evolution of computing then you should consider ClearCube. Well-funded, profitable and experiencing explosive growth, we are always looking for exceptional people to add to our team. Competitive salaries and a comprehensive benefits package make ClearCube a great choice. A fun and challenging work environment make it a compelling one.</p>
                        <p>ClearCube is headquartered in Austin, Texas, an established technology center and one of the country's highest-rated lifestyle cities. We're actively looking for energetic, motivated people who thrive on creativity and responsibility.</p>
                        <p>To join the ClearCube team, where your talent and contribution will be respected, contact us at <a href="mailto:jobs@clearcube.com">jobs@clearcube.com</a>.</p>
                        <p>ClearCube Technology is an equal opportunity employer.
                        </p><br />
                        </div>
