<h3>Engineering Opportunities</h3>
<p>ClearCube Technology, Inc., based in Austin, TX, is the market leader in centralized computing solutions, providing organizations full control over end user computing. An established, fast-growing company, ClearCube has it all – bright, innovative people working on leading-edge software and hardware solutions, a multitude of impressive customers, and an enjoyable culture based on open communication and teamwork.</p>
